Package: escenic-content-engine-installer
Version: VERSION
Depends: escenic-common-scripts (>= VERSION)
Section: base
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: MAINTAINER_NAME <MAINTAINER_EMAIL>
Description: The Escenic Content Engine Installer.
  The ece-install script lets you install the Escenic Content Engine,
  its plugins and Widget Framwork. It will also allow you to install
  the database, cache and web servers.
  .
  The script can run in both interactive or full automatic mode (FAI). See the
  documentation in /usr/share/doc/escenic/ for further details.

